						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1445 (1524 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Records a gift of 174 cows to the goddess for milk-food. Mentions probably as the donor, Teṉṉavaṉ Brahmārāyar Tirumalai Aḻagiya Perumāḷ Raṅgar. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1445, Subhānu, Māśi, 20 ••• dasi,</hi> are insufficient for calculation. <hi rend="bold">The details</hi> correspond to <hi rend="bold">1524 A.D., February 15, Monday,</hi> on which day <hi rend="bold">the</hi> <hi rend="italic">tithi</hi> was <hi rend="italic">ēkādaśī.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
